Localization.Name: Nivala Shoes Ash
Localization.Description: The Alejo Brothers expertly engineered the Nivala shoes to provide high ankle support while remaining lightweight. The shoes mix the company's patented FullFlex rubber with synthetic nubuck leather for flexible yet strategic support, and feature cushioning on the heels and balls of the feet for supreme comfort.
